  <h1 id="greeting">Charlotte</h1>

<p> Charlotte is located in the U.S. state of North Carolina. The city is ranked #15 by population. According to the 2010 Census, the population was 731,424. </p>

<p>
  The 2019 population estimate was 885,708.
  Charlotte has a land area of 305.4 sq mi, and the population density per square mile is 2,757/sq mi. </p>


